Description:
This was my older brother's shirt.  I don't remember him wearing it, but it is definitely from the 70s. A groovy green and white pattern with green and gold strips.  Ribbed neck and sleeves.  It's perfect for the cool kid with a retro style.  
No tag to identify the material, but it is soft and there is a texture to the fabric that creates the pattern.  
Colors are green, white and gold.  
No stains or marks.  
No repairs.
One pen sized hole on the neck ribbing (see pic) and a tiny pull that you have to look for.
Kept its shape and colors over the years.
